'''Calian''' was the language of the [[Calian]]s of [[Shiva IV]]. As they were from a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] far from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic's]] reaches, Calians never knew [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa's]] [[Translatacomp/Legends|translatacomp]] didn't have Calian registered in its database. However, Leia managed to learn it quickly.

